<TEXT>
<P>
Country music singer Reba McEntire was married over the weekend to Narvel 
Blackstock, her manager, it was announced Monday. The couple was married 
Saturday in Lake Tahoe at a ceremony attended by family members only. McEntire 
was divorced in January, 1988, from her first husband, rodeo star Charlie 
Battles. Blackstock also had been married once. ALEENE MacMINN 
</P>
