17,000-mile flight. KEN HIVELY / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Tony Aliengena, 
left, and pen pal Roman Tcheremnykh grin after landing in Salt Lake City. 
GEORGE FREY; Photo, Signing scroll in Salt Lake City are Jevin Ferguson, left, 
Kelly Ferguson, Audrey Lym. ; Photo, Gary Aliengena discusses first leg of 
flight with son, Tony, in Salt Lake City hotel room. 
